                <h1>The Role and Responsibilities of a Modern Prince</h1>
                <p>A prince is not just a royal title but a symbol of future leadership and responsibility. Often steeped in tradition, a prince must balance duty with personal desires. They undergo rigorous training in diplomacy, governance, and cultural heritage, preparing them to inherit the throne and serve their kingdom with honor and integrity.</p>
